{
    "publish_date": "2012-06-28T18:50:17.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT5M43S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "it is always now", 
            "dur": "4.381", 
            "start": "0.719"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "i actually want to talk", 
            "dur": "1.55", 
            "start": "5.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "today about death", 
            "dur": "4.149", 
            "start": "6.65"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "now most of us do our best to not to\nthink about death", 
            "dur": "3.11", 
            "start": "10.799"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but there&#39;s always part of our\nminds that knows", 
            "dur": "3.391", 
            "start": "13.909"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "this cant go on forever", 
            "dur": "1.68", 
            "start": "17.3"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "part of us always knows", 
            "dur": "2.08", 
            "start": "18.98"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that we&#39;re just a doctor&#39;s visit away or\na phone call away from being starkly", 
            "dur": "4.229", 
            "start": "21.06"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "reminded", 
            "dur": "1.181", 
            "start": "25.289"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with the fact of our own mortality", 
            "dur": "3.899", 
            "start": "26.47"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or of those closest to us", 
            "dur": "2.741", 
            "start": "30.369"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "now i&#39;m sure many of you in this room\nhave experienced this in some form", 
            "dur": "5.14", 
            "start": "33.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you must know how uncanny it is", 
            "dur": "2.77", 
            "start": "38.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to suddenly", 
            "dur": "1.9", 
            "start": "41.02"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "be thrown out of the normal course of your life", 
            "dur": "4.12", 
            "start": "42.92"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and just be given the full time job\nof not dying", 
            "dur": "4.18", 
            "start": "47.04"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or caring for someone who is", 
            "dur": "2.74", 
            "start": "51.22"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but the one thing people tend to realize", 
            "dur": "3.98", 
            "start": "53.96"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "at moments like this is that they wasted\na lot of time", 
            "dur": "3.72", 
            "start": "57.94"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when life was normal", 
            "dur": "2.17", 
            "start": "61.66"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it&#39;s not just what they, it&#39;s not just what they did with their time, it&#39;s not just", 
            "dur": "3.02", 
            "start": "63.83"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that they", 
            "dur": "1.05", 
            "start": "66.85"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "spent too much time working or or\ncompulsively checking email", 
            "dur": "3.78", 
            "start": "67.9"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s that they cared about the wrong things", 
            "dur": "3.69", 
            "start": "71.68"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they regret what they cared about", 
            "dur": "4.78", 
            "start": "75.37"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "their attention was bound up in petty concerns", 
            "dur": "3.809", 
            "start": "80.15"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "year after year", 
            "dur": "3.131", 
            "start": "83.959"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when life was normal", 
            "dur": "3.11", 
            "start": "87.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and this is a paradox of course because", 
            "dur": "2.56", 
            "start": "90.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we all know", 
            "dur": "1.16", 
            "start": "92.76"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "this epiphany is coming", 
            "dur": "2.83", 
            "start": "93.92"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "i mean, don&#39;t you know this is coming?", 
            "dur": "3.08", 
            "start": "96.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "don&#39;t you know there&#39;s going to come a day", 
            "dur": "3.41", 
            "start": "99.83"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when you&#39;ll be sick or someone close to you will die", 
            "dur": "3.29", 
            "start": "103.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you&#39;ll look back", 
            "dur": "1.81", 
            "start": "106.53"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "at the kinds of things that captured\nyour attention", 
            "dur": "4.54", 
            "start": "108.34"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you&#39;ll think, &quot;what, what was I doing?&quot;", 
            "dur": "5.13", 
            "start": "112.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you know this, and yet if you&#39;re like most people,", 
            "dur": "3.49", 
            "start": "118.01"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;ll spend most of your time in life", 
            "dur": "3.82", 
            "start": "121.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "tacitly presuming you&#39;ll live forever", 
            "dur": "2.979", 
            "start": "125.32"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s like watching a bad movie for the fourth time", 
            "dur": "5.491", 
            "start": "128.299"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or bickering with your spouse", 
            "dur": "2.569", 
            "start": "133.79"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I mean this, these things only makes sense", 
            "dur": "2.53", 
            "start": "136.359"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in light of eternity", 
            "dur": "1.791", 
            "start": "138.889"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "there better be a heaven if we&#39;re gonna\nwaste our time like that", 
            "dur": "4.989", 
            "start": "140.68"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "there are ways to", 
            "dur": "1.671", 
            "start": "145.669"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "really live in the present moment", 
            "dur": "4.459", 
            "start": "147.34"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what what&#39;s the alternative?", 
            "dur": "4.29", 
            "start": "151.799"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it is always now", 
            "dur": "4.52", 
            "start": "156.089"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "however much you feel you may need to\nplan for the future", 
            "dur": "2.93", 
            "start": "160.609"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to anticipate it, to mitigate the risks,", 
            "dur": "2.77", 
            "start": "163.539"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the reality of your life is now", 
            "dur": "4.9", 
            "start": "166.309"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "this may sound trite", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "171.209"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but it&#39;s the truth", 
            "dur": "2.51", 
            "start": "174.209"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s not quite true as a matter of physics, in fact there is no now", 
            "dur": "3.93", 
            "start": "176.719"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that encompasses the entire universe you\ncan&#39;t talk about an event", 
            "dur": "3.27", 
            "start": "180.649"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "being simultaneously", 
            "dur": "1.54", 
            "start": "183.919"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "occurring here and one", 
            "dur": "2.71", 
            "start": "185.459"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "at the same moment occurring in Andromeda", 
            "dur": "4.1", 
            "start": "188.169"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the truth is, now is not even\nwell-defined as a matter of neurology because", 
            "dur": "4.57", 
            "start": "192.269"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we know that inputs to the brain", 
            "dur": "2.61", 
            "start": "196.839"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "come at different moments and that \nconsciousness is built upon layers", 
            "dur": "4.51", 
            "start": "199.449"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of inputs whose timing to have to be\ndifferent", 
            "dur": "3.331", 
            "start": "203.959"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "are conscious awareness of the present\nmoment is", 
            "dur": "2.58", 
            "start": "207.29"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in some relevant sense already a memory", 
            "dur": "4.359", 
            "start": "209.87"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but as a matter of conscious experience", 
            "dur": "2.58", 
            "start": "214.229"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the reality of your life", 
            "dur": "2.39", 
            "start": "216.809"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is always now", 
            "dur": "3.481", 
            "start": "219.199"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and i think this is a liberating truth\nabout the nature of the human mind in", 
            "dur": "3.129", 
            "start": "222.68"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "fact i think there&#39;s probably nothing\nmore important to understand", 
            "dur": "4.54", 
            "start": "225.809"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "about your mind than that", 
            "dur": "2.3", 
            "start": "230.349"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if you want to be happy", 
            "dur": "4.37", 
            "start": "232.649"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the past is a memory", 
            "dur": "3.02", 
            "start": "237.019"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s a thought", 
            "dur": "1.39", 
            "start": "240.039"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "arising in the present", 
            "dur": "2.78", 
            "start": "241.429"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the future is merely anticipated, it\nis another thought", 
            "dur": "4.19", 
            "start": "244.209"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "arising now", 
            "dur": "3.4", 
            "start": "248.399"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what we truly have", 
            "dur": "3.39", 
            "start": "251.799"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is this moment", 
            "dur": "3.381", 
            "start": "255.189"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and this", 
            "dur": "1.809", 
            "start": "258.57"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and this", 
            "dur": "5.241", 
            "start": "260.379"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and we spend most of our lives forgetting this truth", 
            "dur": "3.379", 
            "start": "265.62"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "repudiating it, fleeing it, overlooking it,", 
            "dur": "3.211", 
            "start": "268.999"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the horror", 
            "dur": "2.429", 
            "start": "272.21"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is that we succeed", 
            "dur": "2.53", 
            "start": "274.639"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we we&#39;ve managed to", 
            "dur": "2.08", 
            "start": "277.169"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "never really connect with the present\nmoment and find fulfillment there because we", 
            "dur": "4.02", 
            "start": "279.249"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "are we are", 
            "dur": "1.9", 
            "start": "283.269"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "continually hoping to become happy in\nthe future", 
            "dur": "4.87", 
            "start": "285.169"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the future never arrives", 
            "dur": "4", 
            "start": "290.039"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "even when we think we&#39;re in the\npresent moment we&#39;re, we&#39;re in very", 
            "dur": "2.96", 
            "start": "294.039"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "subtle ways, always looking over its\nshoulder", 
            "dur": "2.881", 
            "start": "296.999"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "anticipating what&#39;s coming next", 
            "dur": "2.909", 
            "start": "299.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we&#39;re always solving a problem", 
            "dur": "3.22", 
            "start": "302.789"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it&#39;s possible to simply drop your\nproblem", 
            "dur": "3.53", 
            "start": "306.009"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if only for a moment", 
            "dur": "1.451", 
            "start": "309.539"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and enjoy whatever is true of your\nlife in the present", 
            "dur": "5.37", 
            "start": "310.99"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "this is not a matter of new information", 
            "dur": "3.47", 
            "start": "316.36"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or more information, it requires a\nchange in attitude", 
            "dur": "5.349", 
            "start": "319.83"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it requires a change in the attentiveness you pay", 
            "dur": "4.19", 
            "start": "325.179"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to your experience in the\npresent moment", 
            "dur": "1.67", 
            "start": "329.369"
        }
    ], 
